On Wed, 1 Jun 2005 VWBrain(-at-)aol.com wrote:

> ...I also prefer to use the super clips . these have a spring type
> loop that enables you to lightly wire tye the clip...

I use the standard circlip, and then safety-wire it on with wire through
the holes on the end of the clip.  I also put a loop of safety wire around
the throwout bearing and through the holes on the throwout bearing spring
clips, keeping them in place.

George
